  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Girls&apos; Period protection in schools-Minembwe-DRC</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Around 1,000 girls in Minembwe Highlands miss a week of school per month because of period and lack of access to suitable hygiene products. A feeling of shame and absence of hygiene products that lead to gradual drop-out reduce the girls&apos; chances to succeed in school.  This girls Hygiene Kit assistance consists to distributing washable pads to 250 girls and promoting good practices in schools and villages on menstruation to improve girls&apos; living conditions and school success in Minembwe.</narrative>
  </description>
